OL,3,CLorry driver crashes into car and
OL,4,Cnarrowly misses family while on phone
OL,6,FCredit: CPS/Media Wales
OL,8,FA lorry driver seen repeatedly looking
OL,9,Fat his phone before crashing into a
OL,10,Fstationary car has been given an 8
OL,11,Fmonth suspended prison sentence.
OL,13,F44-year-old Raymond Catterall from
OL,14,FMerseyside was driving along the A55
OL,15,Fnear Bangor when his 7.5 tonne lorry
OL,16,Fcollided with the broken down car last
OL,17,FMay.
