OL,3,CLorry driver crashes into car and
OL,4,Cnarrowly misses family while on phone
OL,6,FIn the moments leading up to the
OL,7,Fcrash, footage from the lorry's cabin
OL,8,Freveals Catterall was repeatedly
OL,9,Flooking down at his phone.
OL,11,FDashcam footage also shows how he
OL,12,Fnarrowly avoids a family as his lorry
OL,13,Fswerves into the verge.
OL,15,FCatterall pleaded guilty to a
OL,16,Fdangerous driving charge and using a
OL,17,Fmobile phone at the wheel.
