OL,6,FA judge at Caernarfon Crown Court
OL,7,Fhanded down an 8 month prison
OL,8,Fsentence, suspended for 18 months and
OL,9,Fordered Catterall to do 150 hours of
OL,10,Funpaid work and wear a tag during a
OL,11,Fcurfew.
OL,13,FHe has been disqualified from driving
OL,14,Ffor a year and must pass an extended
OL,15,Fretest.
